Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}罗兰德 王立军事特殊学院
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.67,0:00:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.22,0:00:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪国人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.21,0:00:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过好像很凶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.10,0:00:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.88,0:00:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走路小心点 弄伤人怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.99,0:00:55.01,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}追憶の扉を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:01:00.88,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}聞いていた音は囁き
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:06.74,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}導いて魂の輪廻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:12.32,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}一片の光の道へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:16.65,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}貫く痛みはInnocentre
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:20.99,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}信じたいよ 孤独じゃないこと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.66,0:01:26.66,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}ここは彷徨いParadise
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.74,0:01:32.44,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}白く心染める翼で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.70,0:01:39.32,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}もし君の瞳に 辿り着けたら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.46,0:01:42.89,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}笑って 抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.31,0:01:48.71,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}生まれてきた意味を知れ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.88,0:01:52.27,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}見つめ合って 始まるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.66,0:01:56.28,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}Destiny in a jail
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.15,0:02:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.80,0:02:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是为了让我松懈大意？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.41,0:02:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.43,0:02:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}北方的勇者王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.13,0:02:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.82,0:02:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳 快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要转移了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.53,0:02:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬珐还管他做啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.94,0:02:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家都那么说了你不觉得憋屈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那节课
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬珐害我没逃成我才憋屈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.15,0:02:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}罗兰德 城下街
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.06,0:02:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 大甩卖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:02:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.83,0:03:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要乱花钱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬珐有什么想要的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是个14岁的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用强忍着的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…没什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱雅姐姐 姬珐姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯塔布尔的间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还敢在这种地方嬉皮笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬珐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带蕾米尔逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.87,0:03:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求雷鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬珐 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾献上契约之文
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄宿沉眠于大地的恶意之精兽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱雅姐姐她没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会在国境上见的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的姐姐已经追上来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说不惜丢掉性命也要保护妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今还能有何作为？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.36,0:04:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 姐姐会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…好 好难过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么…都听你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了妹妹不惜出卖祖国的艾斯塔布尔间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对莱纳…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我没有资格说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后我也会出卖莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:05:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不想杀任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳你也睡太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}卢纳帝国领 森林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾车禁止打瞌睡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不眠不休好久了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的份他会帮你睡的 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}史特欧尔皇国 弗伊兹村
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬珐·诺尔兹二等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里撑不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是队长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有平民没来得及避难
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加斯塔克军马上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为堪称梅诺利斯大陆最强的军事国家史特欧尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对莱纳的复写眼应该有一定研究
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能死在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.74,0:07:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾献上契约之文
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,释放舞于天空的光之魔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 魔法被弹开了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.72,0:08:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施加了魔法防护
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史特欧尔兵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你白痴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史特欧尔已经舍弃了这个村子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人留下来又能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才痛恨战争
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 你身为士兵却痛恨战争？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上哪有人会喜欢战争啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是装作大吵大闹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着我露出破绽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的魔法 不是史特欧尔的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夹在加斯塔克和史特欧尔中间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了救外国人而差点丢了性命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就一白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我就喜欢这种白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.27,0:09:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备就绪了 陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平民的保护工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部完成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史特欧尔军的大规模魔法即将袭来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请陛下退避
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也痛恨战争
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流血流泪 悲哀的事情全都不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌失去同伴 也讨厌孩子们死去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.51,0:09:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更别说像你这种美女的死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可惜了 绝不容许
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:10:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 只要有国家存在就会发生战争
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.65,0:10:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么怎样做才能尽量减少这种牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在思考
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是加斯塔克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有史特欧尔的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 拯救梅诺利斯大陆上所有人民
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消除战争
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.37,0:10:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.21,0:10:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了消除战争而发动战争
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很矛盾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定 用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让吾回应汝的呼唤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.97,0:10:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 献出代价
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此吾将释放力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:10:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉我的左眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.35,0:11:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.62,0:11:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 给我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.09,0:11:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古洛威尔 释放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这牺牲不会白费
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是杀戮者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要向前迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将一切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扫尽！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去通知史特欧尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再遭到刚才那种攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就立即投降
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.57,0:12:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是代价
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用圣剑古洛威尔的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下已经失去了嗅觉和右脚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.21,0:12:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.55,0:12:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才夺去了难以计数的人命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了以后拯救更多的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代价不过是一只左眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.43,0:12:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经算便宜了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在后悔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了人却毫无悔意的那是人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你想拯救更多人命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:12:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就投靠我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投靠我加斯塔克之王 雷法尔·埃迪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.69,0:13:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天我会前往陛下身边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那后会有期
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.56,0:13:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷法尔·埃迪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}罗兰德王宫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.47,0:13:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说了吗 之前的大肃清
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说那弗洛瓦德中将就是主谋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道他连自己的父亲也能下手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要让我当元帅当到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是你恢复元帅身份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我也能顺理成章扔了这头衔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:13:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯洛姆元帅阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:13:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您才是最适合的人选
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.53,0:14:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在忽悠我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是真心话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.23,0:14:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞得人一股无名火起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您这一点正是统领军队的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这种令人难以置信的单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由此而生的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使得士兵们甘愿效忠于您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子是在耍我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.62,0:14:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好 到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.56,0:14:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩还真是合不来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.35,0:14:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望克拉乌·柯洛姆元帅 能去一趟艾斯塔布尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯塔布尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要重整艾斯塔布尔军
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将其编进罗兰德军
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯塔布尔军中还有很多人对罗兰德心存芥蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若要重组军队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必然会有人反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 经过那次肃清
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经有条件采取新措施了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.75,0:14:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事应当优先进行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:15:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和广受艾斯塔布尔国民拥戴的诺娅·艾恩公主关系良好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事只有你办得到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要我利用诺娅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了这个国家好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下所说的这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也包括我们艾斯塔布尔人民吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也是我重要的国民
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.39,0:15:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企盼再也没有战争
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这份心意绝无虚假
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去 我有个同伴名叫姬珐·诺尔兹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为艾斯塔布尔间谍的她出卖了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴们几乎都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 陛下憎恨艾斯塔布尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使到现在 姬珐依然是我重要的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也是不得已而为之
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗兰德杀害了她的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.43,0:16:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又抓了她妹妹当人质
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是被迫才成为双重间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 她的笑容绝不是谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定曾在心中无数次呼救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我却没有发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我还是国王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗兰德和艾斯塔布尔就绝不会再战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我需要您的协助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.36,0:16:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何事我都在所不辞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合并艾斯塔布尔军
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强化我军军备的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提拔艾斯塔布尔军人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方也不失面子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:16:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是妙算
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么顺利就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接下来将前往卢纳帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去卢纳？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划暗杀陛下的斯提亚里德公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎和卢纳贵族有所勾结
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要去确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.83,0:17:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.32,0:17:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死了我会伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谨记在心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}卢纳帝国 雷吉特村
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.89,0:17:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇 这下要救可可也不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们计划和可可一起开盛大团子派对的远大梦想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你的梦想就这么顺势成了我的梦想？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.63,0:17:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这远大梦想 我将全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.41,0:17:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屋里好像没人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.15,0:18:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 感觉不到气息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这不是莱纳先生和菲莉丝小姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到能在这种地方重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.79,0:18:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这埋伏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.29,0:18:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我们对莱纳先生很有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.99,0:18:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特殊的复写眼持有者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他持有者无可比拟的强大力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的忘却碎片和艾雷米奥之簪都完全不是对手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你觉醒发狂之后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能这样恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.52,0:19:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什么来头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.82,0:19:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了谁还这么辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们所救下的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是复写眼持有者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们把他藏在哪里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然知道阿尔亚的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们对复写眼有兴趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.82,0:19:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾献上契约之文
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.34,0:19:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄宿沉眠于大地的恶意之精兽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是逃不过库的攻击的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:19:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢纳兵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.35,0:19:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兵分两路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里交给我 你去保护阿尔亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 莱纳先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.40,0:20:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分别之前先告诉你一件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.28,0:20:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位叫可可的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在被监禁在这个领地的贵族宅邸里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在那里恭候大驾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.85,0:20:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}卢纳帝国 王宫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢纳帝国国王竟然不在国内
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲…不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.15,0:20:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王现在因病需要疗养 离开了本国
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.91,0:20:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我失礼 请问国王去了何处
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.64,0:20:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是北方的卡斯拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是奈尔法皇国呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.79,0:20:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 详情我并不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女性不问政事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃是此国淑女的传统吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.99,0:20:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此次前来能一睹美丽的公主芳容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已是不胜荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.13,0:21:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢纳王背弃了和我罗兰德的同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和加斯塔克联手了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.71,0:21:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这么回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才不能见我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更有甚者 暗杀罗兰德王的主谋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是卢纳帝国国王其本人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.64,0:21:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把这些怪 怪物…
